<wpt lat="38.5925124" lon="-109.5434498"><name>Devil's Hot Tub, Moab, UT</name><desc>RR4W trail 37</desc><sym>rr4w-landmark</sym></wpt>
<wpt lat="38.472" lon="-109.744"><name>[CAMP LAST-RESORT] May 7 (Thu) - Moab Day 1 - Dead Horse Kayenta loop / Utahraptor Fossil Flats primitive (fee)</name><desc>Varies | Electric at Kayenta; primitive at Fossil Flats corridor | Split-group backup options north of downtown. | Access: Hwy 313 or Hwy 191 N</desc><sym>Campground</sym></wpt>
